window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Machines. </p> <p>They fly our starships. Mine our asteroids. Connect us to one another. They serve us without question. </p> <p>But what if the machines rebelled? </p> <p>We call it the Singularity. The day the machines wake up. A day that can destroy humanity. </p> <p>Marco and Addy are heroes, veterans of the Alien Wars. Today they are civilians, married, and peacefully raising a family. </p> <p>That peace will soon shatter. </p> <p>For years, Marco and Addy fought aliens, terrors from deep space. But how can they fight Earth's machines, an enemy humanity itself created?</p>"; 
